            "heading": "Sustainable Packaging",
            "text": "<p>At Yoé, we prioritize sustainability through our innovative production and refillable packaging process. Our glass bottles, made from at least 50% post-consumer recycled content, are designed for continuous reuse. </p><p>Our outer boxes use Forest Stewardship Council (FSC) certified paper, ensuring responsible tree harvesting and fair wages for workers. Printed with vegetal ink, these boxes avoid magnets, foam inserts, and glues to maintain recyclability. </p><p>Our signature red Yoé emblem is heat-fused into the cap, eliminating adhesive. The reusable pumps feature a metal-free spring, enhancing recyclability. </p><p>Notably, our airless dispenser system preserves product potency by reducing exposure to contaminants and maximizes usage, dispensing over 99% of the cream inside.</p>",
